title: you know what?
body:
it’s bucky’s fault. it’s all bucky’s fault. 

if he hadn’t fallen off that train, he would still be steve’s top priority. peggy wouldn’t have moved to first place. bucky would’ve grown old with steve and loved each other until they died of old age.

if he hadn’t fallen off that train, hydra wouldn’t have captured him and turned him into the winter soldier. he wouldn’t have assassinated tony’s parents. steve wouldn’t have someone to fight for. civil war wouldn’t have taken place.

if he hadn’t fell off that train, then he and steve would’ve defeated red skull much, much sooner. steve wouldn’t have been on that crashing ship and wouldn’t have frozen. steve wouldn’t have been in the avengers.

what i’m trying to say is is that bucky shaped the future.
